      Ensures that the assignment of a sequence of variables is recognized by CAUTOMATON, a deterministic finite automaton, and that the sum of the costs associated to each assignment is bounded by the cost variable.

      Ensures that the assignment of a sequence of VARS is recognized by CAUTOMATON, a deterministic finite automaton, and that the sum of the cost vector COSTS associated to each assignment is bounded by the variable vector CVARS.
